    "name": "Half Away",
    "steam_appid": 3323500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/d3ecdc07df7f572a9555e4ea4795118a.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/d3ecdc07df7f572a9555e4ea4795118a.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=84 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Half Away</i></strong> is a Narrative Puzzle-Adventure set in a vibrant realm inspired by <strong>Slavic</strong> and <strong>Japanese</strong> folklore. Journey with Juna as she navigates the Spirit Realm, using her unique power to hear hidden voices and connect with <strong>spirits</strong> on a path of self-discovery and choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Juna</strong> awakens in a mystical forest with no memory of arriving, only a faint recollection of being ill. She soon realizes she's in Limbo, a land where spirits dwell and where humans rarely tread. To return to life, she must embark on a journey of ancient mysteries, mystical powers, and encounters with spirits, both kind and mysterious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/74074e258957657151ae0819a99a5b24.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/74074e258957657151ae0819a99a5b24.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will <strong>Juna</strong> return home, or stay in <strong>Limbo</strong> to aid both <strong>spirits</strong> and <strong>humans</strong>, shaping the events of the <strong>living world</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/bf2f791a176f4044542782d6caf547fa.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/bf2f791a176f4044542782d6caf547fa.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=84 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/636a5f238db931a7f4b1095947f6f082.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/636a5f238db931a7f4b1095947f6f082.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               Explore the <strong>fragmented lands</strong> of Limbo, where <strong>ancient spirits</strong> reside and hidden                         secrets await. Uncover their stories and unravel the mysteries of this mystical                           world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/9696509505a45da3f26c7057fbf926f3.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/9696509505a45da3f26c7057fbf926f3.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/44374a4e7d6a781f1fe45bdb6e80f7c4.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/44374a4e7d6a781f1fe45bdb6e80f7c4.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=61 /></span>              <strong>Listen to objects</strong> in the world to uncover hidden details and collect vital information.                Every discovery is recorded in your <strong>journal</strong>, providing clues that guide your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/09ab54bbad16f170b7c41f3537296b58.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/09ab54bbad16f170b7c41f3537296b58.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/ac50df800673f9b86345daa87326f3a1.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/ac50df800673f9b86345daa87326f3a1.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=61 /></span>             Embark on a branching journey with key decisions that influence Juna’s path and the               fates of spirits and humans, shaping the story’s outcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/8ac173973748ee52aec96bec77e6ab3f.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/8ac173973748ee52aec96bec77e6ab3f.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/a7f131424c7f5a2a8552a800383d0546.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/a7f131424c7f5a2a8552a800383d0546.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=61 /></span>            Solve <strong>puzzles</strong> with the help of friendly spirits and the power of <strong>Resonance</strong>.                                By listening  the hidden voices of the world, you can unlock secrets and overcome                    environmental challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/f97d3070ddd39f60d6136996ac4f5de0.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/f97d3070ddd39f60d6136996ac4f5de0.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/2fc2960a62dec18e3cce4ecf75e397d8.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/2fc2960a62dec18e3cce4ecf75e397d8.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           Uncover four unique endings as you solve puzzles with the guidance of friendly spirits             and the power of Resonance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/c23b8d4a24f19433e5e03b36ab987144.poster.avif?t=1771599313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/c23b8d4a24f19433e5e03b36ab987144.webm?t=1771599313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/7b1a6fe5111d596370ee04550be24c6f.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/7b1a6fe5111d596370ee04550be24c6f.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect a deeply narrative-driven experience, where most of the game focuses on storytelling. Puzzles play a secondary role and are not the core focus. Created by a small indie studio, the game is designed to be a short and meaningful experience, as we chose to focus on crafting a compact journey for our first game.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/532cee297cce23c0abf16fc33d39d709.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/532cee297cce23c0abf16fc33d39d709.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras/3d0a7481bacac91df73f800588958d82.avif?t=1771599313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323500/extras_big/3d0a7481bacac91df73f800588958d82.avif?t=1771599313 width=800 height=52 /></span></p>",
